      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，半加器和全加器是作为两个独立的子图放在math_adder_basic这个大容器里吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "math_adder_basic",
        "Half_Adder",
        "Full_Adder"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，math_adder_basic是顶层，下面挂两个子图：一个叫Half Adder，一个叫Full Adder。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "math_adder_basic",
        "Half_Adder",
        "Full_Adder"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先把这两个子图搭好。Half Adder里面需要放哪些节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Half_Adder"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "半加器有三个节点：输入端HA_IN标注A,B；输出一个是和HA_SUM，公式是A异或B；另一个是进位HA_COUT，公式是A与B。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HA_IN",
        "HA_SUM",
        "HA_COUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "HA_SUM是Sum = A ^ B，HA_COUT是Cout = A & B，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HA_SUM",
        "HA_COUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。然后全加器类似，但是多了一个进位输入Cin。FA_IN是A,B,Cin；FA_SUM是三个数的异或；FA_COUT复杂一点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FA_IN",
        "FA_SUM",
        "FA_COUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "FA_COUT的公式您能再说一遍吗？是(A与B)或上什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FA_COUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Cout = (A&B) | (Cin&(A^B))，就是要么前两个产生进位，要么Cin和异或结果产生进位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FA_COUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
